<!-- /wp:image --></div>
<!-- /wp:column --></div>
<!-- /wp:columns -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Click on the Toolkit topics to learn more about TA2TA and its online resource center, the TA provider community, and project implementation.</p>
